task.summary: Default task

Many changes. Functions to deal with timelapses and multiple stage positions; func to save jpegs; possible temporary addition to n2 analysis func; completely new segmentation algorithm; a few misc functions
Re-segmented and analysed all data
changes to scriots
Changes to scripts
Changes to analysis scripts: more class based, save data as txt files, analysis results in separate directory to main data folder. Changes to figure scripts: now saves plots as png
Changes to make more compatible with server
Changes to analysis scripts: more class based, save data as txt files, analysis results in separate directory to main data folder. Changes to figure scripts: now saves plots as png
Changes for cluster
classes for segmentation, analysis, batch analysis
Scripts now save parameter files for each embryo folder, before performing analysis on all
Moved scripts to new project
Fixed glitch in segmentation algorithm, added option for periodic vs non-periodic segmentation

Added generic segmenter class containing shared methods between segmenter subclasses. Segmenters now interpolate fitted coordinates to one pixel distances, ensures even coverage by quantifier. Ability to specify initial ROI within python, and fit spline to this. For segmenter1: end-fit and gaussian fit functions incorporated into single function. Added segmenter4 method to align coordinates to peak of profiles (useful for segmenting membrane background curves). Added segmenter5: segmentation using cytoplasmic and membrane background curves. Quantifier performs seperate calculations for anterior, posterior and whole membrane signal intensity. Function to calculate average membrane concentration, based on shape and assuming rotational symmetry + similar changes to whole embryo dosage calculation. Tidied section at end for general array functions.
Added readme (currently empty) and example scripts for two segmentation methods
Added 2-channel plots for 2-channel segmentation methods, plot_straight method, Segmenter6 subclass (two channel)
Large restructuring
Big tidy. Removed old segmenter/quantifier classes
Removed some unused functions
Changed profile fit method, changed default parameters. Quantifier now saves 2d 'images' of fitted profile and components
Stopped end-fixing, cubic interpolation
Fixes for non-periodic segmentation. Parameters for savgol smoothening
